## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of current data and the diversity of perspectives in the sources consulted. Some sources may have inherent biases, and the legal and ethical landscape of euthanasia is continually evolving, which may not be fully captured in this report. Additionally, cultural and regional differences in the perception of euthanasia are not extensively covered.